  <refentry xml:id="function.quotemeta" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>quotemeta</refname>
    <refpurpose>Quota i meta caratteri</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>Descrizione</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>string</type><methodname>quotemeta</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>str</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     Restituisce una versione di <parameter>str</parameter> con il carattere backslash
     (<literal>\</literal>) davanti ai seguenti 
     caratteri: <screen>. \ + * ? [ ^ ] ( $ )</screen>
    </para>

    &note.bin-safe;

    <simpara>
     Vedere anche <function>addslashes</function>,
     <function>htmlentities</function>, 
     <function>htmlspecialchars</function>, 
     <function>nl2br</function> e
     <function>stripslashes</function>.
    </simpara>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

